B.a2l=new A.ab(-301,B.b5,461,'"Contrary to standard operating procedures" means:',B.WC,1,B.A,null,null,null)
B.Wv=s(["The main cause was crew rest","Crew rest was one element that made the accident more likely","Crew rest alone caused the accident","The crew rested adequately"],t.s)
B.a2g=new A.ab(-302,B.b5,462,'"A contributing factor was the inadequate crew rest period." This means:',B.Wv,1,B.A,null,null,null)
B.Te=s(["It is confirmed that","There was not enough evidence to establish","It is unlikely that","The investigation did not examine"],t.s)
B.a20=new A.ab(-303,B.b5,463,'"It could not be determined whether\u2026" in a report means:',B.Te,1,B.aY,null,null,null)
